Package: sshm
Version: ${VERSION}
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: ${ARCH}
Maintainer: Sn0wAlice <github@sn0w.io>
Homepage: https://github.com/Sn0wAlice/sshm
Description: Fast, modern SSH host manager for the terminal
 SSHM is a terminal UI application to manage, organize, and connect
 to your SSH hosts. Features include fuzzy search, nested folders,
 host reachability checks, port forwarding, theme customization,
 and export to ~/.ssh/config format.
